nodes.title: T2V Prompt
widgets_values: Mid shot, f11m_n01r film noir, 1940s aesthetic, cinematic. The camera lingers in the dim interior of an old house and focuses on the front door, the walls are lined with faded wallpaper peeling at the edges. A single table lamp flickers weakly, casting long, jagged shadows across dusty furniture. The air is thick with the scent of aged wood and forgotten memories. The front door creaks open, and the camera tightens on a captivating 29-year-old brunette, her face framed against the neon-lit downpour. Raindrops trickle from the brim of her wide hat, the shadow partially obscuring her sharp, knowing eyes. The lens lingers as she steps forward, her gaze locked, lips subtly parted, a flicker of intrigue in her expression. The shallow depth of field blurs the storm behind her, drawing every detail of her face into striking focus.

I recommend using the LSDIR upscaler, get it here: 
https://openmodeldb.info/models/4x-LSDIR
